{
  "stem": "8916.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father was working at Schindler's company and my brother was with Schindler's company.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At first they were living in Plaszow and going back and forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then when this sub camp was created, my brother and my father went to live in that sub camp in Schindler's company.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother and I were in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Emalia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my sister, as you know, was still at this cable company or the electrical appliance company.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- I got my brush making job back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother was still working as a cleaning lady.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were doing cleaning in the-- inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Schindler as-- after he built his sub camp decided to increase his workforce and was taking on more people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my father asked him to put my mother and me on the-- on the list.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As you can see, there were several Schindler's lists, you know, not-- not just one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For example, when my brother was taken-- was added to the Schindler's company, that was another list because my father asked him to take my brother on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when the next group was going to be sent to Schindler's company, then a list was created of those people who were going to be sent.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the-- on the-- on Schindler's company I was-- I only had a number when I went on the last-- on the last leg of our trip, that is the one where we moved the company from Krakow to Plaszow because at that point, we went through a-- Gross-Rosen camp.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- there we got an actual number.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before that, all we had was a letter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a letter tattooed on our arm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "K-- K-- K-- KL, I guess it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
